properties.Text:
INSERT INTO ${table} (
	prediction_date,
	prediction_time,
	date,
	time,
	location_name,
	technology,
	longitude,
	latitude,
	precipitation_mm,
	snow,
	ice,
	lightning,
	hail,
	temperature_c,
	windspeed_m_s,
	windspeed_100m_m_s,
	windgusts_m_s,
	fog,
	condition,
	visibility_km,
	source	
) VALUES (
	'${start_date}'
	,'${prediction_time}'
	,'${forecast_basis_date:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'NULL'
	,'${location_name}'
	,'${technology}'
	,${longitude}
	,${latitude}
	,${precipitation_mm:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,'${snow:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${ice:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${lightning:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${hail:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,${temperature_c:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${windspeed_km_h:replaceNull('NULL')} / 3.6
	,${windspeed_100m_km_h:replaceNull('NULL')} / 3.6
	,${windgusts_km_h:replaceNull('NULL')} / 3.6
	,'${fog:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,'${condition:replaceNull('NULL')}'
	,${visibility_km:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,'${source:replaceNull('NULL')}'
);
